## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0110e-349">これと同じ、<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Name%2A>のプロパティ、<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.SchemaEntry%2A>プロパティです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0110e-349">This is the same as the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Name%2A> property of the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.SchemaEntry%2A> property.</span></span>  

